channel.title: Packing models
channel.description: Hey so I just added the completionist cape to my server [pi]. I added the completionist cape models into the cache located in my C:\Users\Username. I then created a new client for my players to download with the completionist cape ints. The problem is, the other players who play my server can't get the new cache with the completionist cape models to download. They tried deleting and re-installing the cache but that didn't change anything. I don't know how to get their clients to download the new cache with the new models. Any help?
